`tests/test_sampler_dispatch.py` are comprehensive, using a mock OSC client to verify message ordering and content.\n\n## Issues Found\n- None.\n\n## Verdict: PASS\n\n## Notes for Lead Agent\nThe implementation is solid. The seed `FX_PRESETS_BY_MODE` table is correctly positioned for future expansion in T-020.\n","file_path":"sdp/verification/t-003@20260425t183959z-verify.md"}}
